Package: herald.rules
Type: Package
Title: Validation Rules Data for the 'herald' Package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Vignesh", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "vthanik@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: Provides pre-compiled validation rules, submission profile
    configurations, and CDISC controlled terminology for use with the
    'herald' clinical dataset submission package. Includes 3,593 rules
    covering CDISC conformance (CDISC Library), FDA Business and Validator
    rules, PMDA rules, NCI EVS controlled terminology, and Herald-original
    gap-fill rules. Bundling rules as a CRAN data package ensures fully
    offline operation, version-pinned reproducibility, and compliance with
    air-gapped pharmaceutical validation environments.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: xz
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
    herald,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
URL: https://github.com/vthanik/herald-rules
BugReports: https://github.com/vthanik/herald-rules/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Config/testthat/edition: 3
